br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1139882\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1139882</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2019年 4月<br />\n<br />\nGoogle封鎖Android App開發商 因被發現與中國政府共享所搜集的資訊!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1139900\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1139900</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\nGoogle Play Store 把大量中國廣告詐騙 App 下架<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1120048\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1120048</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2019年 3月<br />\n<br />\nGoogle Play成惡意軟件SimBad溫床 全球1.5億應用程式使用者中招<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1080068\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1080068</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\nAndroid 4.4 及更高系統存漏洞，會被黑客盜竊手機用戶私隱！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1080060\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1080060</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n網絡釣魚郵件假冒Google的reCAPTCHA系統<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1041289\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1041289</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2019年 2月<br />\n<br />\n研究：逾1.8萬款Android程式可建立裝置的活動紀錄<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1039659\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1039659</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n打開PNG就被黑客入侵？Android 再爆漏洞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1022858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1022858</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n月燒 10GB 流量！ Google Play 又被發現手機 App 詐騙廣告<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1038628\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1038628</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2018年尾<br />\n<br />\nGoogle Play 毒 App 被下載超 58 萬次，Google 後知後覺急下架！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/918524\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/918524</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\nAndroid 用戶注意！新病毒展開攻擊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/785838\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/785838</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n3星用家下載要塞英雄要小心惡意程式<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/801379\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/801379</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\nGoogle推新功能拎個人資訊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/801386\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/801386</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4d8a81fe02ec305b0c2b48fd11bba872f7d8ed93","tid":1142252,"uid":109383,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"aaec89a13fbaeabef5875171347b649bb27236a6","tid":1142252,"uid":132326,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"67a948dc5df43f7cf08afb65e0867eec990ed4d9","tid":1142252,"uid":162866,"like":359,"dislike":12,"score":347,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T03:13:59.000Z","msg":"唔係幫大陸但係你對住支mic講google ads都會跟你講過D乜show乜出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T05:50:53.000Z","msg":"up得就up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T05:54:58.000Z","msg":"自己google下囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有幾難？"},{"pid":"16dc6d10fd0d62c8814a48f32590639abe0817ef","tid":1142252,"uid":86509,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"67a948dc5df43f7cf08afb65e0867eec990ed4d9","tid":1142252,"uid":162866,"like":359,"dislike":12,"score":347,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T03:13:59.000Z","msg":"唔係幫大陸但係你對住支mic講google ads都會跟你講過D乜show乜出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T06:11:35.000Z","msg":"Google錄音要授權喎<br />\n支那你想避<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bfbe6ccd93603d6a205a0465431acd3c6eb72a4","tid":1142252,"uid":43314,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"9232334e3059c985476834254756de0e18f50640","tid":1142252,"uid":77143,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T03:51:48.000Z","msg":"facebook google一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=