765cfbf4df0f612345b17ef2798511808f687","tid":1142252,"uid":155919,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67a948dc5df43f7cf08afb65e0867eec990ed4d9","tid":1142252,"uid":162866,"like":359,"dislike":12,"score":347,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T03:13:59.000Z","msg":"唔係幫大陸但係你對住支mic講google ads都會跟你講過D乜show乜出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T06:35:03.000Z","msg":"google有晒由2012 年起你所有o既語音記錄，你可以自己download番黎聽"},{"pid":"7445ffb7e1d3a09bc8c9c69c0c14d77a6d648aa3","tid":1142252,"uid":21481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T06:36:32.000Z","msg":"ios會唔會安全啲"},{"pid":"bfebe9e0aaac8ad105ac91262e8376ac10bed412","tid":1142252,"uid":29625,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"b519d4b08cb8c525fc439d60fb2f20172b004241","tid":1142252,"uid":55010,"like":16,"dislike":8,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T04:32:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/piLrsjp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpiLrsjp.jpg&h=ddf36259&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實有幾多人會入去睇清楚人地寫咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大陸app冇得揀，人地Google放哂俾你揀，仲有嗰個人化廣告可以關，成日話人偷睇你，你第五人格都要Google play game 做登入，實你有玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T06:45:06.000Z","msg":"其實收集嘅數據呢度只係佔一少部分<br />\n你知唔知你上緊嘅網絕大部分都有include google, facebook同一大堆公司嘅javascript或者其他resources?<br />\n用呢個方法收集data已經好耐歷史<br />\n以連登為例:<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/WuLNcah.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FWuLNcah.png&h=c116105e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n只要你上連登嘅時候無block到<br />\n呢堆公司就有機會得到你嘅browsing history, IP, geolocation, device info等等大量資料<br />\n係呀呢啲資料未必係經你個google account授權去拎到<br />\n但係只要將2邊data對比一下，已經可以間接地將呢啲資料同你個google account link埋<br />\n<br />\nfacebook就係好例子，就算你無account都好<br />\n佢都會透過唔同方法收集你嘅資料再建立一個shadow profile:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/2018/4/11/17225482/facebook-shadow-profiles-zuckerberg-congress-data-privacy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2018%2F4%2F11%2F17225482%2Ffacebook-shadow-profiles-zuckerberg-congress-data-privacy&d=BbGirfR5U81eMP64OYU5HHvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=b89f414d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.theverge.com/2018/4/11/17225482/facebook-shadow-profiles-zuckerberg-congress-data-privacy</a><br />\n仲未計啲公司會將呢啲data不斷轉手，你根本唔知自己嘅資料會俾人賣咗去邊<br />\n<br />\n雖然近幾年社會對私隱關注度係高咗<br />\n但係其實大眾對呢個問題認知仲係好片面，上面只係講咗冰山一角<br />\n有興趣可以自己做下research<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e2ce1bdeb68cadfdf5940bd2843ab0afde0e485","tid":1142252,"uid":110832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T06:46:55.000Z","msg":"同google一鳩樣<br />\n<br />\n不過支那app會俾中共查<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7d01711bc15a5fbbbdd8b00e3d5d71927627abb","tid":1142252,"uid":79410,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4d8a81fe02ec305b0c2b48fd11bba872f7d8ed93","tid":1142252,"uid":109383,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"aaec89a13fbaeabef5875171347b649bb27236a6","tid":1142252,"uid":132326,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"67a948dc5df43f7cf08afb65e0867eec990ed4d9","tid":1142252,"uid":162866,"like":359,"dislike":12,"score":347,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T03:13:59.000Z","msg":"唔係幫大陸但係你對住支mic講google ads都會跟你講過D乜show乜出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T05:50:53.000Z","msg":"up得就up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T05:54:58.000Z","msg":"自己google下囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有幾難？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T06:47:22.000Z","msg":"記得前一排有人開post講過。<br />\n我就試下係咁對住部電話講AV無碼AV無碼AV無碼。一日講咗過百次<br />\n到而家一個av廣告都冇彈過出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"h